Who: RODIMUS, Darkhawk,

> "Havent you noticed that she's the ONLY female in this Alfa male Pack?" said
> Darkhawk as if Rodimus had missed somethign bovious"She will get a lot
> attention"

Rodimus glared at Darkhawk, "Watch yourself." he said, his hands
tightening. Rodimus glanced down at the security monitor and sure
enough noted Cyclonus standing with Nightlight, uncomfortably close!
His hands clenched!

He was about to storm into the throne room when Hydras' call came through.

> "You Two Stop to Chit chat"said By comlink Hydras"Rodimus, you are in charge
> of Security, go to control Room and start your duties; Perceptor, I need you
> to do some errands in throne room; Scourge and Darkhawk start to do Guard"

"Yes sir." Rodimus said through clenched teeth, it was obvious that he
was angry and tense, but something in him forced him to do Hydras'
bidding. Part of himself hated that, his optics glowed dangerously.

"You will pay for this Cyclonus." he said mumbling under his breath.
"You had better not be trying anything with her." he said as he exited
out of the door on the way to the control room. "or we will be doing
more than talk next time."

Of course Cyclonus couldn't hear him. he hated that too.

(TAG)

Preston
